### Model Development Roadmap (from AIOC+ Concept Review)
The AI plan follows a versioned model + edge deployment sequence:

| Phase | Description |
|---|---|
| **AI Model V0** | Train a baseline pedestrian model using **existing OC data** to establish initial quality/perf targets |
| **Edge V0** (D + 4 wks) | Stand up basic AI pipeline: ingest video, run model on-device, upload detections to cloud |
| **AI Model V1** | Fine-tune to AIOC+ optics & platform using AIOC+ field data |
| **Edge V1** (D + 8 wks) | Deploy improved model + integrate PW state machine for better filtering & alert quality |
| **AI Model V2** | Use more AIOC+ field data to improve precision/recall; lock GA-candidate model |
| **Edge V2** (D + 12 wks) | Ship GA model with production-grade telemetry and remote tuning |

