### Software Phasing
- **Beta (target: Sep 15)**: Software must support pedestrian detection — detect pedestrians and **draw bounding boxes on in-cab display** video output.
- The MVP in-cab display will show pedestrian overlay on relevant cameras (bounding boxes only — no full warning state machine yet at Beta).

