### Key Technical Challenges

| Challenge | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Platform migration** | Prior pedestrian work was on **Ambarella** framework; AIOC+ runs on **Qualcomm** — datasets and annotations are reusable but need porting |
| **Different camera** | AIOC+ uses **third-party AHD/TVI analog cameras** (vs. the inbuilt VPU camera on OC1) — perspectives, FOV, and image characteristics differ significantly |
| **Data gap** | New AIOC+ field data will be needed to properly tune after baseline model |
| **Resourcing** | Not currently in plan; AI resources need to be freed up or added — this is the gating factor |

